title: FOX MTB Presents | Kirt Voreis and Tyler McCaul Test New Fox AM/TR Gear in Bend, Oregon
description:
Check out Kirt Voreis and Tyler McCaul ripping on trail bikes in Bend Or.
We tested the 2013 Fox All Mountain, and Trail gear while shooting this fun video.
